Summary: Two objects following same path and disappeared
divs: Sighting DetailsAt 9:40 I was outside using sky safari, then suddenly noticed a moving object coming from the north heading south. Then a second object, exactly the same and on the same path. They both seem to disappear in the same location as if they had gone higher. Definitely not a plane or firework. Both objects were probably visible for a minute at most.
